reviews.review_text: China doll so good. you are all missing out if you're not following Matthew's work. I still can't show that mine is the only view yet.This stuff is heaven. I only got to 80 or so shows. 86- 91. a few before, but . I met Brent ,Billy, Mickey, and Bob. We.just stayed at same places they did. met at bars after the shows. Like at the Ritz in Chicago for axample.They were and are.just people making music. cool dudes. One time late at night, Brent asked.me if he had to play later or had a day off. I laughed, that dayMikey, Brent a few of my other buds went boating o n Lake Geneva. Great times. I miss them. Always thememories. so again. Thank you Matthew
